PORT CONFIGURATION COMMAND
==========================

Command Description
-------------------

See IHUB Interface Guide and IHUB QoS Guide for more information. The command 
can be accessed and executed by operators with link privileges.


User Level
----------

The command can be executed by operators with link privileges.

Command Syntax
--------------

The command has the following syntax:
> configure port
